Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on using a mobile robot to collect data for model-based learning of turbulent flows. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper utilizes Gaussian Processes and Bayesian inference to construct statistical models of the flow properties. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although not explicitly mentioned, computer vision techniques may be used to aid in the robot's navigation and data collection. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses controlling the mobile robot through a sequence of waypoints to maximize the information content of the measurements. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): Although not explicitly mentioned, the use of a mobile robot could be considered a form of multi-agent system.
